<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ zài nǎ lǐ 迦南1255</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 chéng qiáng bèi huǐ chóu dí gōng jī zhǔ a shì wǒ men dé zuì le nǐ
 de tǔ huāng liáng xiǎo yáng mí lí pú táo yuán zhōng jìn rù le hú lí
 shéi zài kū qì shéi zài kū qì dài qiú de shēng yīn rú cǐ qīng zhé
 zhǔ qiú nǐ shè miǎn zhǔ qiú nǐ xìng qǐ jīn rì de ní xī mǐ nǐ zài nǎ lǐ
 yáng de hǎo mù rén nǐ zài nǎ lǐ shén jiā de hǎo dì xiōng nǐ zài nǎ lǐ
 nǐ zài nǎ lǐ nǐ zài nǎ lǐ de tǔ huāng liáng xiǎo yáng mí lí</lyrics>
